OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start in places but
OL,6,Fsoon turning cloudier as rain spreads
OL,7,Feast in the morning. A drier afternoon
OL,8,Fwith some bright spells developing,
OL,9,Fespecially towards eastern coasts
OL,10,Fwhere it will feel warm. Breezy at
OL,11,Ftimes.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be a largely dry
OL,14,Fevening with late bright or sunny
OL,15,Fspells and winds falling light.
OL,16,FRemaining dry overnight with clear
OL,17,Fspells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
