OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA dry morning with some bright
OL,6,Fspells at first but turning
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy. This leads to a
OL,8,Fcloudy afternoon with rain spreading
OL,9,Feastwards.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,12,Fcloudy and breezy Monday and Tuesday
OL,13,Fwith the best of any bright spells in
OL,14,Fthe east. Rain at times, particularly
OL,15,Fin the west. Dry with longer sunny
OL,16,Fspells Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
